metadata.name: Men of Tsuki
metadata.description:
As the earth's atmosphere became unlivable part of the human population fled to start a new life on the moon (Tsuki).  Using all their knowledge and resources, they developed new technologies and exploited new sources of energy that allowed them to adapt quickly to the moon's atmosphere. The biggest supplier of energy on the moon is what they call " The holy tree".  The technology behind this plant is highly confidential and not disclosed to the public. Men of Tsukiâ€˜s physical features altered with time. Their body parts extend because of the absence of gravity and their skin is almost white due to the absence of contact with direct sunlight.

Men of Tsuki Features: (Scale 1 to 10) 
Intelligence 8/10
Adaptation 9/10
Strength 3/10
Agility 4/10

GAME ALERT: Each piece contains clues about upcoming worlds and species. If a collector manages to guess the next species or world after 3 attempts only, the collector with the most guesses would win a surprise piece at the end of the collection.
